commit.title: Remove -compat 8.7
commit.message:
Remove -compat 8.7

This should not be merged until shortly before branching v8.11.

This removes various compatibility notations.

Closes #8374

This commit was mostly created by running `./dev/tools/update-compat.py
--master`.  There's a bit of manual spacing adjustment around all of the
removed compatibility notations, and some test-suite updates were done
manually.
